            <div class="title">
                The War
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1939-12-14/debates/46bf158d-f819-48ba-ba31-b3152155b445/MilkPricesAndAgriculturalPolicy" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
